    <td class='rst'>Call routine at address 0030h: RST 30</td>
    <td class='load'>Add signed 8-bit immediate to SP and save result in HL: LDHL SP,d</td>
    <td class='load'>Load HL to SP: LD SP,HL</td>
    <td class='load'>Load A from given 16-bit address: LD A,(nn)</td>
    <td class='nil'>Enable interrupts: EI</td>
