<p>I am Arnaud Jean-Baptiste, I have a PhD.</p>

<p>Since March 2013, Iâ€™m  post-doctoral at INRIA Lille in the RMod teamÂ direct by Stephane Ducasse. </p>

<p>The goal of RMoD is to support remodularization of object-oriented applications. This objective is tackled from two complementary perspectives: reengineering and modularity constructs for programming languages. I am assign to the SafePython Project.</p>

