#



### Ressources:
[jenkins](https://ci.inria.fr/pharo-contribution/view/RaspberryPi/job/RaspberryPi-Compilation/);T;
I"Õ<h1 id="configure-raspbian">Configure Raspbian</h1>

<p>#</p>

<h3 id="ressources">Ressources:</h3>
<p><a href="https://ci.inria.fr/pharo-contribution/view/RaspberryPi/job/RaspberryPi-Compilation/">jenkins</a></p>;T;@nI"/crosscompileraspbian/;T{;{	;I"Ñ+<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
